### Get Category by Slug
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/slug/electronics
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Category by Slug - Fashion
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/slug/fashion
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Category by Slug - Not Found
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories/slug/non-existent-slug
Accept: application/json
